C + Dust = CD
CD + X = CdX
CdX + N = Cdxn
Cdxn + N = Cd10
Cd10 + Cd10 = Cd20

5 - Cd11:

CD + X = CdX
CdX + N = Cdxn

Cd10 + CdX = Cd11

5 - C-n-wind:

N + X-sea = N-sea
N-sea + Wind = N-wind
C-Sea + N-wind = C-n-wind

5 - N-sex:
